item.title: Servers dont work
item.dc:creator: @KillerbeeWon KillerbeeWon
item.description:
@KillerbeeWon wrote:

[quote=“jen itohls, post:1, topic:114797”]Whenever I put in the information and click enter, it says the server is down on every server, and below it says Error:Unable to startup listener 43594 - port already in use?
Someone know what it means?[/quote]
Yeah, that means you already have your server started. Or, another window of your server is up. Only one at a time.
